latestIgtvVideos.title: Borg, Teddy, Boucle Headboard DIY HACK for under £20
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I purchased this Teddy thow from @dunelmuk and a fabric staple gun and made this headboard revamp! 
.
I can’t believe how well it turned out! Especially the border! If you use a smaller headboard than a super king then the border will have to wrap round the back to be stapled and won’t show, but will still trying be beautiful and a cleaner line! 
.
I made this purchase late a night when I couldn’t sleep and had this lightbulb idea when I was lusting after high end versions of the trendy Teddy furniture! I can’t say I have seen many headboards!
.
I will do another video of a few more details on how I did this but DM me for any questions and feel free to share with any of your DIY lovers! 
.
Don’t forgot the use the right side of the throw as the other side looks more fluffy than this! 
.
